Package: eurodata
Title: Regional Indicators from Eurostat for EU27 NUTS-2 Regions
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Giampaolo", "Montaletti",
           email = "giampaolo.montaletti@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0002-5327-1122"))
Description: Collects regional (NUTS-2) indicators from Eurostat for EU27
    countries, transforms them into a unified schema, selects a peer group
    of regions comparable to a reference region, and exports the results.
